86void
87dns_log_init(isc_log_t *lctx);
88/*%
89 * Make the libdns categories and modules available for use with the
90 * ISC logging library.
91 *
92 * Requires:
93 *\li lctx is a valid logging context.
94 *
95 *\li dns_log_init() is called only once.
96 *
97 * Ensures:
98 * \li The categories and modules defined above are available for
99 * use by isc_log_usechannnel() and isc_log_write().
100 */
101
102void
103dns_log_setcontext(isc_log_t *lctx);
104/*%
105 * Make the libdns library use the provided context for logging internal
106 * messages.
107 *
108 * Requires:
109 *\li lctx is a valid logging context.
110 */
111
112ISC_LANG_ENDDECLS
